    <h1>Hook</h1>
    <p class="description">The opening line, visual, or moment in a piece of content designed to grab attention within the first 1-3 seconds — before the viewer, reader, or listener decides to scroll past, close the tab, or keep going.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
